						<span class="related-date">Sep 01, 2025</span>
					</a>
					<a href="/articles/weekend-spotlight-hamptons-guide" class="related-card">
						<h4>Weekend Spotlight: One Thing to Worry About, One Thing to Do, One Thing That Will Make You Say 'Only in the Hamptons'</h4>
						<span class="related-date">Aug 29, 2025</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</aside>
		</div>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
